title: Clubland Classix 2 (3CD)split tracks
description:
The album of your life is back again for the sequel! Bringing together the ultimate hits from the hottest dancefloors across the country, Clubland Classix 2 features 3CDs of top tunes from Scooter, Cascada and Ultrabeat, as well as international stars Lady Gaga and The Pussycat Dolls
